  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Scaling-up of productive water (micro-irrigation) and safe water (households)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">This program will reach 300&#x92;000 farmers with improved micro-irrigation technologies and 3 million poor household with safe water through chlorination. Both parts of this program will be founding partners of emerging global alliances: micro-irrigation with the Gates Foundation and the Dutch DGIS, safe water through the multi stakeholder initiative &#x93;safe water for 300 million in 6 years&#x94;. SDC will be in a good position to influence both alliances and through them the water sector in general. The supply chain approach with the local private enterprises has clearly the potential to reach rapidly a great number of people and global coverage. Micro-irrigation and household water disinfection are strategic activities to reduce inefficiency in the use of water in agriculture and to rapidly improve drinking water quality.</narrative>
  </description>
